<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٣٥ - وَأَسْوَأُ التَّجْرِيحِ مَا قَدْ وُصِفَا … بِـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كَذِبٍ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْوَضْعِ»</span> كَيْفَ صُرِّفَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٣٦ - ثُمَّ بِذَيْنِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«اتَّهَمُوا»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فِيهِ نَظَرْ»</span> … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَاقِطٌ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«هَالِكٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا يُعْتَبَرْ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٣٧ - وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ذَاهِبٌ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَكَتُوا عَنْهُ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تُرِكْ»</span> … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَيْسَ بِالثِّقَةِ»</span>، بَعْدَهُ سُلِكْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣٣٨ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَلْقَوْا حَدِيثَهُ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضَعِيفٌ جِدَّا»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِرْمِ بِهِ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«وَاهٍ بِمَرَّهْ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«رُدَّا»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣٣٩ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَيْسَ بِشَيْءٍ»</span>، ثُمَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا يُحْتَجُّ بِهْ»</span> … كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُنْكَرِ الْحَدِيثِ»</span> أَوْ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُضْطَرِبِهْ»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣٤٠ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«وَاهٍ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضَعِيفٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضَعَّفُوا»</span>، يَلِيهِ … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضُعِّفَ»</span> أَوْ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ضُعْفٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَقَالٌ فِيهِ»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣٤١ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تُنْكِرْ وَتَعْرِفْ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«فِيهِ خُلْفٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«طَعَنُوا»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تَكَلَّمُوا»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَيِّئُ حِفْظٍ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَيِّنُ»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٣٤٢ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَيْسَ بِحُجَّةٍ»</span> أَوِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْقَوِيِّ»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«بِعُمْدَةٍ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«بِذَاكَ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«بِالْمَرْضِيِّ»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
